<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ciao, <delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />!</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah, it's <tag a="110" b="3" />!</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Good evening, <tag a="110" b="3" />!</message>
	<message label="001_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Huh.<delay20 /> I was just thinking about you,<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />, <tag a="110" b="5" />.</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You came by my house the day I
moved to this island, right?<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I had a hard time keeping track of all
of the guests I had that day.<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />People are just drawn to my natural
charm, I guess.</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Now that my place is all set up,<delay8 />
I'm going around introducing myself
to the neighbors.
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />When you're trying to make a good
impression, you wanna look your
very best.
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Luckily, that's never been much
of a problem for me.</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm starting to get the hang of life on
<tag a="110" b="8" />.<delay20 /> It almost feels
like I've always lived here, right?
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />In fact,<delay20 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> I honestly can't imagine what
this island would be like without me.</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm going to spend this week
learning everything I can about
<tag a="110" b="8" />, <tag a="110" b="5" />.<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />If I plan on being this island's
resident arbiter of taste<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I need to know how the great the
task ahead of me truly is.</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Now, <delay20 />onto the matter at hand<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I didn't just say hello to you as an
excuse to see your sparkling smile.<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I actually have a gift for you!<delay20 />
Something to celebrate our
newfound friendship.</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I actually stopped you today to give
you another gift.<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />The first one obviously being my
hard-won loyalty and friendship.</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />!
<delay20 />Voila!<delay frames="40" /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> I hope you know how hard it is
to acquire this kind of thing.
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Put it anywhere you want!<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> By a tree,
in your house, on a hill<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Anywhere!<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />As long as you look at it every day
and think of me,<delay20 /> I'll be happy.</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />So<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />what do you think of the
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />?<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> I was
so excited to give it to you!
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I wanted you to have a gift that
wasn't easy to find around here.</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I gotta say,<delay8 /> the look in your eyes
when I gave you that gift makes all
worth it, <tag a="110" b="5" />.
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />The packing, all the moving,<delay8 /> the loss
of a well-established local fan base<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
I'd do it all again for that moment.<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /></message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I don't think there's any better way
to show you<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> how happy I am to
be living on <tag a="110" b="8" />.
I've got big plans for us,
<tag a="110" b="3" />.<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Big plans!</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Anyway, <tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I hope I'm right in assuming you
want to be best friends.
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I knew it, <tag a="110" b="5" />!</message>
</msbt>